    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Ntfy这个通知服务画一张架构图。整体是一个App包裹起来的结构，里面包含Ntfy主应用、Apache代理，还有一些周边组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "app_wrapper",
        "app",
        "apache_proxy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Ntfy作为核心应用。那入口流量是怎么进来的？需要画一个入口节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inbound_interface"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，加一个inbound_interface作为入口，它接收80和443端口的HTTP/HTTPS流量，同时也处理25端口的SMTP邮件通知。这个接口先连到Apache代理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inbound_interface",
        "apache_proxy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把inbound_interface画出来，用80,443标注连到apache_proxy，另外单独拉一条25端口的线直接到app。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inbound_interface",
        "apache_proxy",
        "app"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Apache代理后面要连到Ntfy应用本身，路径是/*:80，表示所有HTTP请求都转发过去。另外Ntfy需要加粗边框，它是核心节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apache_proxy",
        "app"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已给app应用了strong_border样式，apache_proxy到app的连接也标注了/*:80。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "app",
        "apache_proxy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要一个Apache Prometheus Exporter来采集Apache的指标。它通过use关系使用Apache代理，同时Apache要暴露/.apache/metrics端点给它。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apache_prometheus_exporter",
        "apache_proxy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加了apache_prometheus_exporter，画了双向关系：虚线use从exporter指向proxy，实线从proxy的/.apache/metrics指回exporter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apache_prometheus_exporter",
        "apache_proxy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "证书管理这块，我们需要Certificator组件，它是一个CronJob，定期从Let's Encrypt获取证书。图标上要同时显示cronjob和lets-encrypt。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "certificator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Certificator和Apache代理是什么关系？文件系统共享吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "certificator",
        "apache_proxy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
